name: For the dead travel fast...
description:
Bram Stoker inspired charm bracelet.

Features: 4 picture charms (two containing quotes), 3 black voodoo skulls, 2 large siler colour rose beads, smaller silver colour hearts and 3 large deep red beads with silver detailing. 

T-bar and hoop fastening. 

Heavy silver plated bracelete.

Picture charms are water resistant but not water proof. 

Masures 8 inches, links can be removed if needed.

name: Nevermore
description:
Edgar Allan Poe inspired charm bracelet.

Large lobster claw clasp fastening

Light bracelet, featuring 3 charms - 1 large raven claw, 1 small gilded cross and a small book. 

Features: 2 silver letter words. 'Raven' & 'Never More'.

Colours: Purple, blue, clear & black beads, green & blue clear beads and pearlised shades of grey and purple. 

Measures approx 7 inches - 8.5 inches with chain extender. Links can be removed if required.

name: For the Sub
description:
T-bar and ring style fastening. 

Silver plated heavy bracelet. 

4 Charms, one large key and one Locket  and 2 smaller silver keys. 

Features: 'His' in silver lettering.

Colour tones are lilac, black and silver and clear grey. 

Measures 7.5 inches and links can be removed before postage if required.

name: The Bone Collector
description: Black voodoo skulls, on a silver plated charm bracelet. Two Tibetan silver crosses. The Voodoo skulls each have a fire polished glass bead that swings around.

name: Nautical Wishes
description:
Light charm bracelet.

Large lobster clasp fastening.

Features: 1 large anchor charm, 3 blue shell pieces, buttons, 3 bells, 1 'wish' in silver lettering and various mixed style beads.

Colours: Light blue, dark blue, green. silver, pearlised mint green.

Measures 7 inches, extender links can be added if required.
